    "description": "《宇宙探索家 DX》 是个灵感来自 Freelancer 等游戏，设置在广阔的开放宇宙中的复古太空战斗模拟游戏。 在四种不同的职业中进行选择——战士、商人、坦克或工程师，每个职业都有自己的特殊能力和奖励。 与敌对派系作战、开采和交易资源、定制您的船只等等。 玩家可以选择跟随故事，或者跟着自己的节奏探索宇宙并完成支线任务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/1577541b64eb8527c00204f895266398.avif?t=1772113989\" alt=\"Thrilling Space Combat\" width=780 height=80 /></span> <br><br>以第三、第一、或驾驶舱视角与敌对派系、残酷的海盗和神秘的外星人进行激烈的混战。 利用您的驾驶技能、战术和武器库取得胜利。 无论您喜欢精确打击还是全力火力，战斗系统都能为每位有抱负的太空战士提供激动人心的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/a6743340e4c5be67b8565eeafef1ca98.poster.avif?t=1772113989\" aria-label=\"Third person view of a space dogfight\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/a6743340e4c5be67b8565eeafef1ca98.webm?t=1772113989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/a6743340e4c5be67b8565eeafef1ca98.mp4?t=1772113989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/6a6526d9f1114b33ec0a713524edb9dc.avif?t=1772113989\" alt=\"Endless Customization and Upgrades\" width=780 height=80 /></span> <br><br>从十几艘独特的飞船中进行选择，并用超过 100 种不同的物品定制每艘飞船，以满足您的需求。 升级你的武器、护盾或引擎，成为宇宙中最危险的战士，或者选择牵引梁、隐藏隔间或客舱等交易设备走上走私路线。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/c4a1ad4446e0124b2e21fe4e8f48de9a.avif?t=1772113989\" alt=\"Trade Your Way To Riches\" width=780 height=80 /></span> <br><br>在宇宙市场交易商品、提取有价值的矿物或走私非法商品来致富。 如果你选择走私路线，小心警察巡逻！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/318c4b1b5fdd0e8412d38a920b6ea6d7.poster.avif?t=1772113989\" aria-label=\"View of a menu with tradeable spaceship equipment\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/318c4b1b5fdd0e8412d38a920b6ea6d7.webm?t=1772113989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/318c4b1b5fdd0e8412d38a920b6ea6d7.mp4?t=1772113989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/09d2f70c281a24ae05ea79ce6dbf04f3.avif?t=1772113989\" alt=\"Unleash Your Inner Explorer\" width=780 height=80 /></span> <br><br>在您自己的星船上启航。在各种华丽的空间场景中航行。每个场景都会带来不同的兴趣点。 在安全稳定的星系之间漫游、在独立的边界星球中进行贸易、或者选择海盗星系的冒险。 发现隐藏在宇宙最深处角落的缓存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/4f91029c79617a7e9eefa87d6ef57bbd.poster.avif?t=1772113989\" aria-label=\"A spaceship jumping out of a space gate\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/4f91029c79617a7e9eefa87d6ef57bbd.webm?t=1772113989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/4f91029c79617a7e9eefa87d6ef57bbd.mp4?t=1772113989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/f3d625927e0890253f4febdd6f158ad7.avif?t=1772113989\" alt=\"Experience a Rich Galactic Story\" width=780 height=80 /></span> <br><br>让自己沉浸在《宇宙探索家 DX》引人10小时的游戏和完整配音。 结识魅力四射的人物，揭开古老的秘密，并参与最史诗般的太空战斗。 人类和宇宙的命运掌握在你的手中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/57d2f4f3e8961b7150b2b4e231a50bf4.avif?t=1772113989\" alt=\"Gorgeous Visuals\" width=780 height=80 /></span> <br><br>通过华丽的视觉效果和独特的氛围设计，探索栩栩如生令人惊叹的宇宙。 从广阔的太空到熙熙攘攘的太空港和行星景观，每一个细节都经过精心打造，营造出真正身临其境的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/0f8283d473f6fb30647a0ac6546009c3.poster.avif?t=1772113989\" aria-label=\"Passing between two space cruisers in cockpit view\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/0f8283d473f6fb30647a0ac6546009c3.webm?t=1772113989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/0f8283d473f6fb30647a0ac6546009c3.mp4?t=1772113989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/8b130da6b90e90854afd3779eef8e115.avif?t=1772113989\" alt=\"Get Rewarded in Side Missions\" width=780 height=80 /></span> <br><br>从开采矿物和护送友好船只通过危险区域，到赢得太空竞赛冠军，执行各种支线任务来获取奖励。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401630/extras/2348f607a0f6aedb6cf986b0e3ce144b.avif?t=1772113989\" alt=\"A New Deluxe Experience\" width=780 height=80 /></span> <br><br>《宇宙探索家 DX》对其空间系统、视觉效果和游戏玩法进行了许多改进，以提供全新的豪华体验。 空间系统得到了扩展，增加了新的兴趣点，船只、环境和效果得到了更高层次的重新设计，并且对各种游戏机制、控制和设置进行了改进。",
